RubberBandSelection &ldquo;Rubber-band&rdquo;, or drag-selection is a user-interface feature of GBrowse 1.69 and later. It a javascript/DHTML-based feature that works in all major web browsers and is turned on by default. The purpose of this page is to describe how to control features of the rubber-band selection via the GBrowse configuration-file.
The video below is a demonstration of using the mouse to navigate in GBrowse 2.0
&lt;oflash file=File:Rubberband1.swf width=500 height=275 /&gt;

